title: Ominous Gatekeeper - Six Miles Down The Well (2014)
description:
Ominous Gatekeeper is solo project of Corey Athos (Flesh Consumed, Hydrocephalic, Torturous, etc). We are currently on Unleash the Underground label.

The Gatekeeper guards the entrance to the gates with the dominance of a king. Standing fifteen feet tall, constructed from a vile, depraved, repulsive, abomination. The omnipotent Overlord of Realms, beyond the bounds of hell, allows only the most potent black hearted souls passage.

The key holder to an abyss, apart and beyond the infernal regions known by biblical definition, reigns supreme with staff in hand. With a face of leather, twisted and decrepit, steam pours out of his many nostrils running up his face as incantations pour out his mouth in whisper. The air is foul with decay from breath resembling the aroma of black putrefaction.
